description:
One of the most anticipated episodes, Lip Service veteran Trey Songz stops by and has some interesting conversation with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire. He discusses liking woman who are attentive to details, not marrying a girl who is into 3 sums, having to take 4 paternity tests and even having sex with Gigi's friend while she watched.
